                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240715-118-off630 t18240715-118-cd631"></join>, a handkerchief, value 3 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18240715-118-victim1054" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Goyder
                        <interp inst="t18240715-118-victim1054" type="surname" value="Goyder"></interp>
